<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="297" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="297">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,314,617,642]" pageId="2" pageNumber="297">Diagnosis</emphasis>
(worker). Eyes absent; antennal club 
<number box="[741,752,617,642]" pageId="2" pageNumber="297" value="3.0">3</number>
–segmented; midtibiae covered by short, golden, stout setae; arolia reduced and translucent; ventral petiolar process rounded; body yellow.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
